    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >变成物体以在世界各地执行潜行任务时不被敌人发现。操控环境物体，布置陷阱，并像真正的间谍一样使用各种装备。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163560/extras/5093c485fd608a29e602fcc7317e4605.avif?t=1771801150\" width=600 height=126 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163560/extras/edf31bdcaf4ab35c044afa1e1975ae64.poster.avif?t=1771801150\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163560/extras/edf31bdcaf4ab35c044afa1e1975ae64.webm?t=1771801150\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163560/extras/edf31bdcaf4ab35c044afa1e1975ae64.mp4?t=1771801150\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用你的强大套装变形为不同的物体。仔细选择你要变形的物体，因为套装在使用后需要充电！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163560/extras/923fb53c41c51b3c6b56dd6a1da79cf6.avif?t=1771801150\" width=600 height=126 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163560/extras/272835ad12a1beac813f66af9224153c.poster.avif?t=1771801150\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163560/extras/272835ad12a1beac813f66af9224153c.webm?t=1771801150\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163560/extras/272835ad12a1beac813f66af9224153c.mp4?t=1771801150\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >某些物体具有独特的功能，可以用来操控环境。使用复杂的黑客系统，用发出声音的物体引诱守卫，等等。利用这些额外的能力来应对更复杂的挑战！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163560/extras/6fd94cb4b46a0d553bce792e07364007.avif?t=1771801150\" width=600 height=126 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163560/extras/fcf5f57a7e9d83d59b1ed861377c2319.poster.avif?t=1771801150\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163560/extras/fcf5f57a7e9d83d59b1ed861377c2319.webm?t=1771801150\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163560/extras/fcf5f57a7e9d83d59b1ed861377c2319.mp4?t=1771801150\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每个场景中找到先进的装置和各种物品。使用它们来帮助Siren完成她的任务！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163560/extras/7e0aeaad9f1422e612136982d7e5f9d7.avif?t=1771801150\" width=600 height=126 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163560/extras/6bce024d6858e917f25c3ebcc3b7504c.poster.avif?t=1771801150\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163560/extras/6bce024d6858e917f25c3ebcc3b7504c.webm?t=1771801150\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163560/extras/6bce024d6858e917f25c3ebcc3b7504c.mp4?t=1771801150\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >变形为各种物体并融入环境，避免被发现。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用特殊物体的各种能力来操控环境。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每个章节中使用先进的小工具和各种物品。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在全球各地进行奇特而具有挑战性的任务。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过80个关卡，分为章节，拥有独特的环境、敌人和机制。</p></li></ul>",
